query:
INSERT INTO island_experiences (islandId, experienceId, sortOrder) 
SELECT ig.id, e.id, e.displayOrder
FROM island_guides ig
CROSS JOIN experiences e
WHERE ig.name IN ('Maafushi Island', 'Kandooma Island', 'Thulusdhoo Island', 'Dhiffushi Island', 'Fuvahmulah Island', 'Hulhumalé', 'Ukulhas Island', 'Veligandu Island')
AND e.published = 1
LIMIT 100
